Package cryptoAnalyzer.utils

Class ChartData

  • java.lang.Object
    • cryptoAnalyzer.utils.ChartData
  • public class ChartData
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that implements methods to handle dates and data for the chart and also getter methods to access dates, data, user selections, a row, and a column.

    Author:
